      <title>测试第一篇hexo文章</title>
      <link href="/post/22e9da5d.html"/>
      <url>/post/22e9da5d.html</url>
      
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<body>大家好！我是Egstar</body><pre class="line-numbers language-python" data-language="python"><code class="language-python">$ 这是Python代码哦$ <span class="token keyword">def</span> <span class="token function">hello</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>    <span class="token keyword">print</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token string">"hello Everyone!"</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span>$ 当然这里只是演示啦<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p>怎么实现用户图片的保存和上传呢？</p><p><img src="/images/image-20240509114907775.png" alt="image-20240509114907775"></p><p>可以看到图片已经被保存了</p><pre class="line-numbers language-python" data-language="python"><div class="caption"><span>file.py</span><a href="http://www.baidu.com">hello</a></div><code class="language-python"><span class="token keyword">def</span> <span class="token function">hello</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span>    <span class="token keyword">print</span><span class="token punctuation">(</span><span class="token number">1</span><span class="token punctuation">)</span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p><img src="/images/image-20240509141509890.png" alt="image-20240509141509890"></p><pre class="line-numbers language-Java" data-language="Java"><code class="language-Java">class System()&#123;public void main(String[] args)&#123;System.output.println(&quot;Hello&quot;);&#125;&#125; 当我们调用类执行主程序时,程序会打印hello<span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><p>下面演示的是图库，它使用的html来外挂图片</p><pre class="line-numbers language-markup" data-language="markup"><code class="language-markup"><span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;</span>div</span> <span class="token attr-name">class</span><span class="token attr-value"><span class="token punctuation attr-equals">=</span><span class="token punctuation">"</span>gallery-group-main<span class="token punctuation">"</span></span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span>&#123;% galleryGroup 'ACG' '那些二次元的故事' '/gallery/ACG' https://bu.dusays.com/2022/11/26/638228a86935a.webp %&#125;&#123;% galleryGroup '岳阳' '2017年5月岳阳' '/gallery/YY' https://bu.dusays.com/2022/11/27/63831b681e9f8.jpg %&#125;&#123;% galleryGroup '漫威' '漫威的图片' '/Gallery/marvel' https://i.loli.net/2019/12/25/8t97aVlp4hgyBGu.jpg %&#125;<span class="token tag"><span class="token tag"><span class="token punctuation">&lt;/</span>div</span><span class="token punctuation">></span></span><span aria-hidden="true" class="line-numbers-rows"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre><div class="gallery-group-main">  <figure class="gallery-group">  <img class="gallery-group-img no-lightbox" src='https://bu.dusays.com/2022/11/26/638228a86935a.webp' alt="Group Image Gallery">  <figcaption>  <div class="gallery-group-name">ACG</div>  <p>那些二次元的故事</p>  <a href='/gallery/ACG'></a>  </figcaption>  </figure>    <figure class="gallery-group">  <img class="gallery-group-img no-lightbox" src='https://bu.dusays.com/2022/11/27/63831b681e9f8.jpg' alt="Group Image Gallery">  <figcaption>  <div class="gallery-group-name">岳阳</div>  <p>2017年5月岳阳</p>  <a href='/gallery/YY'></a>  </figcaption>  </figure>    <figure class="gallery-group">  <img class="gallery-group-img no-lightbox" src='https://i.loli.net/2019/12/25/8t97aVlp4hgyBGu.jpg' alt="Group Image Gallery">  <figcaption>  <div class="gallery-group-name">漫威</div>  <p>漫威的图片</p>  <a href='/Gallery/marvel'></a>  </figcaption>  </figure>  </div>]]></content>
      
      
